('579', '6', '621', 'image-alt', 'Images must have alternative text', 'Blocker', '', '4', NULL, 'https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions', 'needs_review', NULL, '6', '2026-02-26 17:23:58', '2026-02-26 17:23:58', 'Ensure <img> elements have alternative text or a role of none or presentation\n\nURL: https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\n\nThe <img> element has no accessible text alternative. Provide one method: <code>alt</code>, <code>aria-label</code>, <code>aria-labelledby</code>, <code>title</code>, or mark decorative with <code>role=\"presentation\"</code>/<code>role=\"none\"</code>.\n- \"img\" in \"VIRTUAL BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER\"', '<img src=\"https://www.samcomf.com/images/career/accordian-arrow.png\" class=\"accordian-arrow\">', '[\"/PMS/uploads/automated_findings/project_6/page_621/20260226_172341_45d308/1772106828443_image-alt_4.png\"]', 'Provide meaningful alt text for informative images and use empty alt (alt=\"\") for decorative images.\n- Write meaningful alt text for informative images and use alt=\"\" for decorative images.\n- Avoid repeating adjacent text in alt value.', '<img src=\"https://www.samcomf.com/images/career/accordian-arrow.png\" class=\"accordian-arrow\" alt=\"Meaningful description\">', '', '{\"rule_id\":\"image-alt\",\"title\":\"Images must have alternative text\",\"severity\":\"critical\",\"needs_review_severity\":\"Blocker\",\"wcag_sc\":[\"1.1.1\"],\"wcag_name\":\"Non-text Content\",\"wcag_level\":\"A\",\"actual_results\":\"Ensure <img> elements have alternative text or a role of none or presentation\\n\\nURL: https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\\n\\nThe <img> element has no accessible text alternative. Provide one method: <code>alt</code>, <code>aria-label</code>, <code>aria-labelledby</code>, <code>title</code>, or mark decorative with <code>role=\\\"presentation\\\"</code>/<code>role=\\\"none\\\"</code>.\\n- \\\"img\\\" in \\\"VIRTUAL BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER\\\"\",\"incorrect_code\":\"<img src=\\