('581', '6', '621', 'label', 'Form elements must have labels', 'Blocker', '', '8', NULL, 'https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions', 'needs_review', NULL, '6', '2026-02-26 17:23:58', '2026-02-26 17:23:58', 'Ensure every form element has a label\n\nURL: https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\n\nThe form control element is missing an accessible label (visible label or ARIA label association).\n- \"candidate_name\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"candidate_phone\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"candidate_email\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"candidate_location\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"candidate_experience_in_years\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"candidate_relevant_experience\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"notice_period\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"department_position\" in \"section#career_application_form\"', '<input type=\"text\" id=\"candidate_name\" name=\"candidate_name\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"tel\" id=\"candidate_phone\" name=\"candidate_phone\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\" pattern=\"[0-9]{10}\" required=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"email\" id=\"candidate_email\" name=\"candidate_email\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"candidate_location\" name=\"candidate_location\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"candidate_experience_in_years\" name=\"candidate_experience_in_years\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"candidate_relevant_experience\" name=\"candidate_relevant_experience\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"notice_period\" name=\"notice_period\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">\n\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"department_position\" name=\"department_position\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" placeholder=\"\" value=\"\">', '[\"/PMS/uploads/automated_findings/project_6/page_621/20260226_172341_45d308/1772106829168_label_6.png\"]', 'Ensure each form control has a clear, programmatically associated accessible name.\n- Add explicit <label for=\"...\"> for each affected form control with unique id/for mapping.\n- Do not rely on placeholder as label; keep a persistent visible label for all users.\n- Verify clicking/tapping the label focuses the correct field.', '<label for=\"candidate_name\">Candidate Name</label>\n<input id=\"candidate_name\" name=\"candidate_name\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n\n<label for=\"candidate_phone\">Candidate Phone</label>\n<input id=\"candidate_phone\" name=\"candidate_phone\" type=\"tel\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n\n<label for=\"candidate_email\">Candidate Email</label>\n<input id=\"candidate_email\" name=\"candidate_email\" type=\"email\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n\n<label for=\"candidate_location\">Candidate Location</label>\n<input id=\"candidate_location\" name=\"candidate_location\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n\n<label for=\"candidate_experience_in_years\">Candidate Experience In Years</label>\n<input id=\"candidate_experience_in_years\" name=\"candidate_experience_in_years\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n\n<label for=\"candidate_relevant_experience\">Candidate Relevant Experience</label>\n<input id=\"candidate_relevant_experience\" name=\"candidate_relevant_experience\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n\n<label for=\"notice_period\">Notice Period</label>\n<input id=\"notice_period\" name=\"notice_period\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\