('583', '6', '621', 'select-name', 'Select element must have an accessible name', 'Blocker', '', '3', NULL, 'https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions', 'needs_review', NULL, '6', '2026-02-26 17:23:58', '2026-02-26 17:23:58', 'Ensure select element has an accessible name\n\nURL: https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\n\nThe <select> element is missing an accessible name (label, aria-label, aria-labelledby, or title).\n- \"department_position_list\" in \"section#career_vanacies_frm\"\n- \"department_name\" in \"section#career_application_form\"\n- \"source_from\" in \"section#career_application_form\"', '<select class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" id=\"department_position_list\" name=\"department_position_list\">\n\n<select class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form department_name_dropdown\" id=\"department_name\" name=\"department_name\">\n\n<select class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\" name=\"source_from\" id=\"source_from\">', '[\"/PMS/uploads/automated_findings/project_6/page_621/20260226_172341_45d308/1772106830544_select-name_10.png\",\"/PMS/uploads/automated_findings/project_6/page_621/20260226_172341_45d308/1772106830909_select-name_11.png\"]', 'Ensure every <select> element has an accessible name.\n- Add explicit <label for=\"...\"> linked to the <select> id for these controls: \"department_position_list\", \"department_name\", \"source_from\".\n- Keep label text descriptive, visible, and placed close to the field.\n- Ensure each <select> has a unique id and each <label for=\"...\"> points to that exact id.\n- Reference: https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/listbox/', '<label for=\"department_position_list\">Department Position List</label>\n<select id=\"department_position_list\" name=\"department_position_list\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n  <option value=\"\">Select Department Position List</option>\n</select>\n\n<label for=\"department_name\">Department Name</label>\n<select id=\"department_name\" name=\"department_name\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form department_name_dropdown\">\n  <option value=\"\">Select Department Name</option>\n</select>\n\n<label for=\"source_from\">Source From</label>\n<select id=\"source_from\" name=\"source_from\" class=\"form-input validate-input-login-form\">\n  <option value=\"\">Select Source From</option>\n</select>', '', '{\"rule_id\":\"select-name\",\"title\":\"Select element must have an accessible name\",\"severity\":\"critical\",\"needs_review_severity\":\"Blocker\",\"wcag_sc\":[\"4.1.2\"],\"wcag_name\":\"Select element must have an accessible name\",\"wcag_level\":\"A\",\"actual_results\":\"Ensure select element has an accessible name\\n\\nURL: https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\\n\\nThe <select> element is missing an accessible name (label, aria-label, aria-labelledby, or title).\\n- \\\"department_position_list\\\" in \\\"section#career_vanacies_frm\\\"\\n- \\\"department_name\\\" in \\\"section#career_application_form\\\"\\n- \\\"source_from\\\" in \\\"section#career_application_form\\\"\",\"incorrect_code\":\"<select class=\\\"form-input validate-input-login-form\\\" id=\\\"department_position_list\\\" name=\\\"department_position_list\\\">\\n\\n<select class=\\\"form-input validate-input-login-form department_name_dropdown\\\" id=\\\"department_name\\\" name=\\\"department_name\\\">\\n\\n<select class=\\\"form-input validate-input-login-form\\\" name=\\\"source_from\\\" id=\\\"source_from\\\">\",\"screenshots\":[\"1772106830544_select-name_10.png\",\"1772106830909_select-name_11.png\"],\"recommendation\":\"Ensure every <select> element has an accessible name.\\n- Add explicit <label for=\\\"...\\\"> linked to the <select> id for these controls: \\\"department_position_list\\\", \\\"department_name\\\", \\\"source_from\\\".\\n- Keep label text descriptive, visible, and placed close to the field.\\n- Ensure each <select> has a unique id and each <label for=\\\"...\\\"> points to that exact id.\\n- Reference: https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/listbox/\",\"correct_code\":\"<label for=\\\"department_position_list\\\">Department Position List</label>\\n<select id=\\\"department_position_list\\\" name=\\\"department_position_list\\\" class=\\\"form-input validate-input-login-form\\\">\\n  <option value=\\\"\\\">Select Department Position List</option>\\n</select>\\n\\n<label for=\\\"department_name\\\">Department Name</label>\\n<select id=\\\"department_name\\\" name=\\\"department_name\\\" class=\\\"form-input validate-input-login-form department_name_dropdown\\\">\\n  <option value=\\\"\\\">Select Department Name</option>\\n</select>\\n\\n<label for=\\\"source_from\\\">Source From</label>\\n<select id=\\\"source_from\\\" name=\\\"source_from\\\" class=\\\"form-input validate-input-login-form\\\">\\n  <option value=\\\"\\\">Select Source From</option>\\n</select>\",\"help_url\":\"\",\"occurrence_count\":3,\"scan_url\":\"https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\",\"scan_urls\":[\"https://www.samcomf.com/career-open-positions\"],\"raw_nodes\":[{\"any\":[{\"id\":\"implicit-label\",\"data\":null,\"relatedNodes\":[],\"impact\":\"critical\",\"message\":\"Element does not have an implicit (wrapped) <label>\"},{\"id\":\"explicit-label\",\"data\":null,\"relatedNodes\":[],\"impact\":\"critical\",\"message\":\"Element does not have an explicit <label>\"},{\"id\":\"aria-label\",\"data\":null,\"relatedNodes\":[],\"impact\":\"critical\",\"message\":\"aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty\"},{\"id\":\"aria-labelledby\",\"data\":null,\"relatedNodes\":[],\"impact\":\"critical\",\"message\":\"aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty\"},{\"id\":\"non-empty-title\",\"data\":{\"messageKey\":\"noAttr\"},\"relatedNodes\":[],\"impact\":\"critical\",\"message\":\"Element has no title attribute\"},{\"id\":\"presentational-role\",\"data\":null,\"relatedNodes\":[],\"impact\":\"critical\"